                            <comment id="17214839" author="guozhang" created="Thu, 15 Oct 2020 17:03:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;When we introduce the new version 4 in list-offsets in &lt;a href=&quot;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/KAFKA/KIP-320%3A+Allow+fetchers+to+detect+and+handle+log+truncation#KIP320:Allowfetcherstodetectandhandlelogtruncation-ListOffsets&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/KAFKA/KIP-320%3A+Allow+fetchers+to+detect+and+handle+log+truncation#KIP320:Allowfetcherstodetectandhandlelogtruncation-ListOffsets&lt;/a&gt; I think, but we did not get it since it would only affect old clients.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
